title: Hoover WindTunnel® Rewind Plus Bagless Upright: Overheating?
description: Hi Michael, I read your message on Facebook and wanted to help you out with your WindTunnel®. I put together a quick video to help your troubleshoot for clogs that can cause your vacuum to overheat. Let me know if you need any more help. I'm here for you.
